# Detection harness inputs/outputs.
# ONLY DokoDocs-generated synthetic composites + fixture JSON are tracked, under
# test/fixtures/detection/synthetic/. Real dataset images belong in a local
# test/fixtures/detection/raw/ (gitignored) and are NEVER committed — see
# docs/DATASET_NOTICE.md.
test/fixtures/detection/*
!test/fixtures/detection/synthetic/
docs/detection_results/


